	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />OK so the <span class="posthilit">N</span> <span class="posthilit">flag</span> can be used for signed comparaison only if there is no overflow, and there is no way to detect overflow other than using SBC.
<br />How unintuitive.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
